description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=3/3, Mature Content=2/3. Something makes  you angry at your breakfast. You knock it down to the floor. You have never done that before, so you go visit a doctor. He informs you that you have a serious illness and that the only cure is for you to go on dates with numerous attractive women. The Fantastic Fivesome features voice acting from adult industry stars, Mariah Milano, Miko Sinz and Kiki Daire.
